      "settings": {
        "title": "Clinically proven solutions",
        "heading_size": "h2",
        "richtext": "<p>BIRETIX is an innovative skincare range from Cantabria Labs, designed to meet the growing demand for effective, science-led solutions for blemish-prone and acne-prone skin. <br/><br/>Combining RETINSPHERE® Technology, BIOPEP-15 and clinically proven dermatological actives, BIRETIX helps target the key factors associated with blemish-prone skin while supporting the skin barrier. Offering a solutions for prevention, treatment support and maintenance, BIRETIX provides clinics, pharmacies and specialist skincare retailers with a trusted range that delivers visible results and encourages long-term customer loyalty. </p>",
        "narrow_text": true,
        "image_width": "third",
        "image_ratio": "adapt",
